  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个调度器（Scheduler）来管理DMA的读写流程。核心是一个状态机控制器，我暂时叫它FSM Controller，它要协调读写两个方向的数据流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scheduler",
        "FSM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那FSM的输入从哪里来？是否需要先有一个描述符（Descriptor）的入口模块？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DESC",
        "FSM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，需要一个Descriptor Input模块接收外部的描述符包。描述符本身由外部的Descriptor Engine生成，通过descriptor_packet接口送进来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DESC",
        "DESC_ENG",
        "descriptor_packet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我画一个Descriptor Input节点，然后加一个FETCH模块做描述符锁存（Descriptor Latch），这样FSM可以从FETCH拿到稳定的描述符信息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DESC",
        "FETCH",
        "FSM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。FETCH到FSM是控制流，FSM解析完描述符后，要分出两路：Read Interface和Write Interface。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FETCH",
        "FSM",
        "RD_IF",
        "WR_IF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在FSM下面挂出RD_IF和WR_IF两个接口模块。这两个接口后面应该对接实际的读写引擎吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FSM",
        "RD_IF",
        "WR_IF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错。RD_IF通过datard_valid/ready握手信号驱动Read Engine，WR_IF同理用datawr_valid/ready驱动Write Engine。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RD_IF",
        "RD_ENG",
        "WR_IF",
        "WR_ENG",
        "datard_valid",
        "datawr_valid"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Read Engine和Write Engine。注意到这两个引擎完成传输后需要反馈给计数器？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RD_ENG",
        "WR_ENG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，RD_ENG和WR_ENG都要输出done_strobe脉冲，分别驱动Read Beat Counter和Write Beat Counter，用来统计实际的读写拍数。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RD_ENG",
        "WR_ENG",
        "BEAT_RD",
        "BEAT_WR",
        "done_strobe"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我把BEAT_RD和BEAT_WR放在FSM的左侧，它们的输出都连回FSM，这样FSM可以监控进度。需要给这两个计数器加个绿色填充区分一下吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BEAT_RD",
        "BEAT_WR",
        "FSM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好主意，绿色表示状态类模块。另外还需要一个Timeout Counter，防止传输卡死，它也连到FSM。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TIMEOUT",
        "FSM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Timeout Counter已添加。还有别的监控需求吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TIMEOUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要错误聚合。Read Engine和Write Engine各自可能上报datard_error和datawr_error，这些要汇总到一个Error Aggregator，再送给FSM做异常处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RD_ENG",
        "WR_ENG",
        "ERR",
        "datard_error",
        "datawr_error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Error Aggregator已放置，左侧三个计数器/聚合器都指向FSM。现在FSM是核心枢纽了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ERR",
        "BEAT_RD",
        "BEAT_WR",
        "TIMEOUT",
        "FSM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "FSM还需要一个MonBus Reporter，把内部状态通过mon_valid/ready接口导出到外部总线，方便软件调试。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MON",
        "mon_valid",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "MonBus Reporter已添加，输出到MonBus。现在Scheduler子图内部结构基本完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MON",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说Descriptor Engine在外部，但它和DESC的连接关系需要明确画出来。DESC_ENG到DESC是descriptor_packet接口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DESC_ENG",
        "DESC",
        "descriptor_packet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我调整一下：DESC_ENG放在Scheduler子图外面，用虚线或明确标注表示它是外部模块，通过descriptor_packet连到DESC。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DESC_ENG",
        "DESC"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "这样结构清晰了。FSM作为核心，给它加个醒目的样式吧，比如粉色填充加粗边框。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FSM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "FSM已设置为粉色填充、4px边框。BEAT_RD和BEAT_WR用浅绿色2px边框，符合之前的约定。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FSM",
        "BEAT_RD",
        "BEAT_WR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再确认一下数据流向：RD_IF到RD_ENG的datard_valid/ready是双向握手，WR_IF到WR_ENG同理。这些要标注在连线上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RD_IF",
        "RD_ENG",
        "WR_IF",
        "WR_ENG",
        "datard_valid",
        "datawr_valid"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已标注。另外MON到MONBUS的mon_valid/ready也标注了。所有控制信号都清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MON",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
