      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "检查一下完整性：DESC→FETCH→FSM，FSM分出RD_IF/WR_IF/MON，两个接口分别驱动RD_ENG/WR_ENG，引擎反馈done_strobe到计数器，错误汇总到ERR，超时监控到TIMEOUT。",
      "elements_involved": [
