      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "最终调整完成。Scheduler子图包含DESC、FETCH、FSM、RD_IF、WR_IF、MON、BEAT_RD、BEAT_WR、TIMEOUT、ERR、RD_ENG、WR_ENG，外部连接DESC_ENG和MONBUS。",
